Test::Simple, basic utilities for writing tests, 
by Michael G Schwern <schwern@pobox.com>.

Included here the simple way, no installation necessary. 
You do need Perl 5.6

* Full distribution - available http://search.cpan.org/~mschwern/Test-Simple-0.98/lib/Test/More.pm

* License info - http://www.cpan.org/misc/cpan-faq.html#How_is_Perl_licensed

* More Info - http://test-more.googlecode.com/
